snippet.title: Art Fight Duel • Cybersteam - Gameplay
snippet.description:
The imagination of plenty of artists is unleashed in card form! Select your team, draw your cards, and summon an extravagant cast of characters from Art Fight to fight on your behalf!

Made as an homage to Art Fight, an event that pits artists into two teams to draw characters from each other, this card game features the original creations of several participants of the event.

With all that in mind, get ready to attack your opponent, protect your team, use items to turn the tide of the battle, and achieve the highest score you can! Walk over the path to victory that the artists have created for you!

Play it!
